B5sDSVg6Q&oe=674EFC49"}, {"file_name": "CycleBar- Home.png", "id": "522956006795209", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974853_522956013461875_8093803523125335619_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=H5W2kA_-350Q7kNvgF_tm_S&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB-O3V1Ciuf5fHdem4KdohN_X4KqEo5sB8tyOjTl7HzYw&oe=674EFCBB"}, {"file_name": "PB-Callibration.png", "id": "1936493886796191", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982629_1936493890129524_3100247740643681336_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=cHQCOCAX7IkQ7kNvgE2r6_T&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCEo2xRLnXb7dx6JSZcYBLfgRkbVrUVTQVhdFljqFjNbQ&oe=674EE097"}, {"file_name": "CB Screenshot 02.png", "id": "7985742398145636", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974859_7985742404812302_4671278461729422000_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=G08I76g_RVUQ7kNvgHwppA0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB0rSnaOCNzZDux-uw-YBfxBRxWXhbSlsGuiwwOwYA9EA&oe=674EEF0D"}, {"file_name": "CycleBar- Classes.png", "id": "485640274332590", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75269591_485640277665923_6852489760100270909_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3U0T6zYdieoQ7kNvgFA6r5C&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCaHcRNPh7LY2mAJzZpzc5pj3tb5g-W0HmHBlaZLkGlRw&oe=674EF91C"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CB - Cover - Landscape.png", "id": "479642521355102", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974834_479642524688435_7065933209497930161_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Lp5zmWGPcyUQ7kNvgHuN0li&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDFqsa0gkujzeCQKdrsKfv-tSsxN1tU2OCFHU1XXAoLmA&oe=674ED643"}, "display_name": "CycleBar", "keywords": ["fitness", "health", "cycling", "spin", "cardio"], "long_description": "Revitalize your fitness routine with CycleBar on Meta Quest! As the largest spin brand in the U.S., CycleBar delivers an unparalleled indoor cycling experience that combines the thrill of high-energy workouts with the innovation of virtual reality. Whether you're a seasoned cyclist or new to the world of spinning, our app offers a captivating and personalized journey designed to elevate your performance and keep you inspired.\n\n**Key Features:**\n\n- **Immersive VR Rides:** Clip into the first indoor cycling VR app on the Quest and feel the rush of riding with top instructors and fellow cyclists from around the world.\n\n- **Expert Instructors:** Ride alongside professional trainers who motivate and guide you through every pedal stroke, ensuring an engaging and effective workout.\n\n- **Variety of Classes:** Choose from a wide range of rides, including high-intensity interval training (HIIT), endurance rides, themed sessions, and more.\n\n- **Personalized Experience:** Customize your workouts to match your fitness goals, with options to adjust intensity and duration for a tailored ride.\n\nEmbark on an exciting journey to fitness with CycleBar on Meta Quest. Discover the power of movement, connect with a supportive community, and transform your ride into an unforgettable experience. Your adventure starts here\u2014get ready to ride!\n{381239874674871}", "short_description": "CycleBar is the first indoor cycling app on Meta Quest! Rock Your Ride with the largest indoor cycling brand in the U.S. Whether you're a VR enthusiast or a cycling lover, our app offers exhilarating rides led by top instructors, designed to boost your endurance, strength, and motivation. Join a vibrant community, track your progress, and transform your fitness journey with CycleBar's cutting-edge virtual reality experience. Get ready to ride like never before!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://xponential.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.xponential.com